reviewText: Jerome is awesome. This workout was excellent from start to finish! Targeted my entire body top to bottom. I am building strength while reshaping my physique.  I would highly recommend this video.
Great total body workout. From start to finish it's non-stop action. The workouts are about an hour long and intense, but you'll feel super accomplished at the end. Highly recommended.
